      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">Who Reviews the Robot's Work?</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">Agents can write code, draft proposals, analyze data, and generate reports. But who checks their work? The quality assurance problem in AI is not about whether agents can produce output. It is about whether anyone is verifying that output meets the standard.</p>
